      "content": "idk i dont think i can just go to HR. if they're actually tracking me with this promotion, HR is probably part of it too. the thing is, ever since the move, i've noticed these little things... like my coffee orders are always exactly what i like even when i don't tell anyone, and there's always someone \"checking in\" on me by name. it feels less like a promotion and more like they're trying to keep me in a controlled environment so i dont talk. dont you think that sounds more like a setup than a reward?",
